replies.body:
Client freezes, specifically in champion select are usually caused by your client not having a completely stable connection to the servers. Local network settings are usually the culprit, so I recommend ensuring those settings are compatible with our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if this helped resolve the issue.
